  <body>
    <button
      id="infoBtn"
      style="
        background-color: #ddd;
        border: none;
        color: #fff;
        border-radius: 50%;
        width: 25px;
        height: 25px;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: bold;
        cursor: pointer;
      "
    >
      i
    </button>

    <div
      id="infoModal"
      style="
        display: none;
        position: fixed;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        z-index: 9999;
      "
    >
      This is Game Check Brain Storming Behaviour Of User.
      <br />
      In this game there are 5 questions, user have to type their answers into
      the given text box if the answer is match with the system user will get
      one point. Else user can use Hint. and retype the answer. If user guess it
      correctly or misspell the Word, will not provide any points. at the end
      user have to save and go back to Home.
      <br />
      If user quess the correct option will get the point user can skip the
      question if don't know the answer.
      <hr />
      Click in the BOX to close me
    </div>

    <div
      id="member_login"
      style="width: 45rem; margin-left: 25rem; margin-top: 5rem"
    >
      <h1 style="text-align: center">Brain Storm</h1>
      <div style="margin: 0 40px">
        <div class="quiz-container">
          <div id="quiz"></div>
        </div>
        <div id="result"></div>
        <div class="cleaner h10"></div>
        <div class="cleaner h10"></div>
        <button class="BUTTON" id="submit" style="margin-left: 17rem">
          Save
        </button>
        <!-- <button id="retest">Start Again</button> -->
      </div>
      <div class="cleaner h10"></div>
      <div class="cleaner h10"></div>
      <form method="POST" action="/game_3" id="Secondary">
        <input type="hidden" name="correct_score" id="correct" value="" />
        <input type="hidden" name="wrong_score" id="wrong" value="" />
        <input type="hidden" name="hint_score" id="hint" value="" />
        <button
          class="BUTTON"
          type="submit"
          style="margin-left: 19rem"
          id="backToHome"
        >
          Home
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
    <div class="cleaner h10"></div>
    <div class="cleaner h10"></div>
    <script src="/js/app3.js"></script>
